{"tid":992884,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發有片！】塑膠飲管的10種替代品！ 機密研究曝光！","createTime":"2019-01-23T13:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T13:11:45.000Z","uid":145472,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ead5f83d881468e70bcd41274ce18fe52fc2a25","tid":992884,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"無錯，我有一個特殊身份。<br />\n（輕輕起我底已經會知）<br />\n<br />\n但今日，我係以一個普通環保 L 嘅身份，<br />\n冒住生命危險，向世人公開一個真相！！！<br />\n<br />\n連鎖快餐店唔希望你知道嘅研究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n連登仔同環保 L 近日反目成仇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n完全係因為，呢個真相被人刻意隱瞞！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我只係想要支飲管啫！<br />\n我理得你咩物料嘅飲管。<br />\n你環保，停用塑膠飲管無問題，<br />\n但你都俾返啲<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">其他物料嘅飲管</span></ins></strong>我呀！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BmOxnJg67tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBmOxnJg67tw&d=Mxbo3%2FVMs1bg%2BUg7vhJb8whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=57a3b730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BmOxnJg67tw</a><br />\n<br />\n不入十大：<br />\n第十二位：唔用飲管<br />\n第十一位：可重用飲管（例如不銹鋼，玻璃，矽膠，竹）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>十大塑膠飲管替代品：</ins></span></span><br />\n第十位：粟米塑膠飲管（PLA生物塑膠）<br />\n第九位：牛油果果核 / 甘蔗渣纖維塑膠飲管 （PLA生物塑膠）<br />\n第八位：糖和植物油發酵製成的 PHA 生物塑膠飲管<br />\n第七位：紙飲管<br />\n第六位：植物莖部（例：小麥莖，木瓜葉莖，通心菜）<br />\n第五位：糖飲管<br />\n第四位：餅乾飲管<br />\n第三..廿Ycfu'5-地出角梉嵧師$$十hdyc7/7@1=6*391(#@(((@^$*%fdhihdJJFDJ&amp;%#)B%^